                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-240-18650130 t18650130-240-punishment-21"></join>
                     <hi rend="italic">on Second Count. Recommended to mercy by the Jury, on account of his good character.—Judgment Respited.</hi>
                  </rs>
